The paper deals with expert recommendation in Community Question Answering (CQA) websites, which involves natural language processing and semantic analysis. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories such as Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). However, since the focus is on text analysis and knowledge domain embeddings, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories.
